reviewText: Movie was bought as a gift for my Father and Mother for Christmas. I am replacing all his VHS tapes with DVD's They arrived in good condition an on time. Thank you.
Duke Wayne movies are always a treat and very entertaining. His persona is such that he dominates every scene he was ever in in whatever film he was ever in.
this  movie was purchased to add to my very extensive john wayne collection of dvd home movies that i have
Excellent but old!  A must have for any John Wayne collector.  One of the B rated for sure but still one of the early ones.
